INSERT INTO "startups" VALUES(22,'Getable','san francisco',2035,'SaaS',2,'Getable makes renting equipment easy for construction contractors and suppliers.  We are an on-demand equipment rental application and have been called the "Uber for construction equipment."  Getable''s enterprise, B2B platform serves the $41 billion U.S. construction equipment rental market, which is growing at 10% YOY.  The total construction equipment market is $136B and we are powering the trend towards paying for access rather than ownership of equipment.  Getable saves contractors significant time and money procuring, tracking, managing, and paying for rentals across all projects.  Our partners are building bridges, roads, highways, airports, hospitals, and tomorrow''s infrastructure.  It''s an honor to work with contractors and suppliers who are building great things.','http://www.getable.com/','https://d1qb2nb5cznatu.cloudfront.net/startups/i/13302-129e58961178c28adfe0d05345b814a0-medium_jpg.jpg?buster=1422418260',1);
INSERT INTO "startups" VALUES(23,'Buffer','san francisco',2027,'social media',3,'Buffer is the simplest and most powerful social media publishing and analytics platform. We help over 1.8m SMBs, of which 28,000+ are paying to power their social media accounts, publishing over 500,000 posts every day. We have consistently grown 10% MoM on average for the last 24 months, having just crossed $4.6m in ARR.
